title: The report Financial Stability published tomorrow (Central Bank of Iceland)
text: ( Source : Central Bank of Iceland ) 05.10. 2015 The Bank 's Financial Stability report will be published tomorrow, Tuesday 6 October 2015 . It will be presented at a press conference held in the Bank 's Sölvhóll conference room at 10:00 hrs.
